  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 12: Murgtal &amp; Northern Heights</name>
    <desc>Ride through the dramatic Murg valley—a deep gorge cutting into the Black Forest—past a stunning reservoir and up to the ridge, combining valley drama with mountain panoramas.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
